---
//@ts-nocheck
import omOsKort from '../assets/om-os-kort.svg';

import '../styles/effects.css';
import '../styles/global.css';
import '../styles/reset.css';
import '../styles/typography.css';
import '../styles/variables.css';

---


<div class="card-container" style={`background-image: url(${omOsKort.src});`}>
  <ol class="card-text-list">
    <li>Hver gang du bruger <strong>Dankort</strong>, donerer vi 1 øre pr. transaktion.</li>
    <li>Er din <strong>bank</strong> en samarbejdspartner donerer de 1 øre pr. transaktion.</li>
    <li>Hvis du handler i en <strong>butik/webshop</strong> der er samarbejdspartner donerer de 1 øre pr. transaktion.</li>
  </ol>
</div>

<style>
  ol {
  list-style: decimal;
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
}

li {
  padding-bottom: var(--gap-xs);
}
  .card-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 650px;
    aspect-ratio: 1.58 / 1;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card-text-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .card-container {
      padding: 0;
    }
    li {
      padding-bottom:0;
    }
    .card-text-list {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
</style>